/target
# Cargo.lock is committed: reproducible, locked dependency resolution for
# the build/test/clippy gates (cargo … --locked). Do not re-ignore.
*.img
*audit*
.history

# GSI test fixture (downloaded by tests/fixtures/download-gsi.sh).
# AOSP-licensed; not redistributed by this repo. The *.img rule above
# already covers system.img, but be explicit for the .tar / .zip
# intermediate forms as well.
tests/fixtures/*.img
tests/fixtures/*.tar*
tests/fixtures/*.zip
